premise_source_doc_sentence: From Vs. , the song `` Daughter '' received a Grammy nomination for Best Rock Performance by a Duo or Group with Vocal and the song `` Go '' received a Grammy nomination for Best Hard Rock Performance .

Oliver Sean 's third studio album ` So Good '  (  2011  )  hit the Vh1 Top 10 for his single `` Movies '' from the album on 4 June 2011 , Featured album spot at the Virgin Megastores in Dubai , Grammy nomination consideration in nine categories for the 54th Grammy Awards nomination ballots , a Vh1 Specials feature in India and the MTV Europe Music Awards 2012 nomination in the MTV EMA Best India/Worldwide Act category .
In 2012 , Céu received her fourth Grammy nomination for `` Best Contemporary Brazilian Pop Album '' for her critically acclaimed third album Caravana Sereia Bloom .
In 2008 , Céu received a Grammy nomination for `` Best Contemporary World Music Album '' in 2008 for her debut album CéU .
Céu received a Latin Grammy nomination for `` Best New Artist '' of 2006 .
